      | +relationships | 1 |
      | +properties    | 1 |

  @NegativeTest
  Scenario: [18] Fail when creating a relationship without a type
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      CREATE ()-->()
      """
    Then a SyntaxError should be raised at compile time: NoSingleRelationshipType

